    <description>Mouse Without Borders is a project that allows you to reach across your PC's as if they were part of one single desktop. You can move files between the 2 computers simply by dragging them from one desktop to another. In fact you can control up to four computers from a single mouse and keyboard with no extra hardware needed.</description>
    <summary>Mouse Without Borders is a project that allows you to reach across your PC's as if they were part of one single desktop.</summary>
    <releaseNotes>
* Mini SnagIt feature (Ctrl+Shift+S)
* Customize keyboard layout
* Personalize Logon Screen for Windows 8
* Some more options and hotkeys, mouse hover each one on the Settings form for more details. Note: There are three Tabs on the Settings form.
